FAQ&colon;

Q&colon; What is the warranty of your product&quest;

A&colon; We offer one year warranty and lifetime technical support

During warranty period if any part broken due to non-human factors&comma; we will repair or replace it&period;

After one year we also offer professional technical support&comma; if you need some spare parts&comma; we just charge you the real material cost&period;

Q&colon; Can I have my own Logo on the machine&quest;

A&colon; Yes&comma; we can make your Logo and put it on the machine&period; And for some products we have different design and different colors for your option

Q&colon; What is the payment term&quest;

A&colon; The payment term is 30&percnt; deposit and 70&percnt; balance before delivery&period;

After the 30&percnt; deposit we will start production&comma; after finish production we will take photos and videos and every detail you want to see&comma; then you make payment of the 70&percnt; balance&period;

Q&colon; How long I can receive the machine after order&quest;

A&colon; If by air&comma; it is about 5-7 days&period;

If by sea&comma; It depends on which Country are you from and where is your sea port&comma; please ask our sales to check&period; In some countries we can help do door to door&period;

Q&colon; Do you have office in my Country&quest;

